OL,3,CAverage price paid for motor insurance
OL,4,Cjumps by a third in a year
OL,6,FThe average price paid for
OL,7,Fcomprehensive motor insurance was
OL,8,Faround a third (33%) or #157 higher in
OL,9,Fthe first quarter of this year than a
OL,10,Fyear earlier, according to figures
OL,11,Ffrom the Association of British
OL,12,FInsurers (ABI).
OL,14,FBased on analysis of policies sold,
OL,15,Fthe typical price paid in the first
OL,16,Fquarter of 2024 was #635, marking a 1%
OL,17,Fincrease on the previous quarter, the
OL,18,FABI said.
