OL,4,Cjumps by a third in a year
OL,6,FIn the first quarter of 2023, the
OL,7,Faverage premium paid for private
OL,8,Fcomprehensive motor insurance was #478.
OL,10,FThe ABI said the 1% quarterly increase
OL,11,Findicates an easing of the rises seen
OL,12,Fin 2023.
OL,14,FIt said that insurers are continuing
OL,15,Fto absorb growing costs, with the
OL,16,Faverage claim paid rising 8% to reach
OL,17,Fa record of #4,800 over the same
OL,18,Fperiod.
