OL,6,FThe association has previously cited
OL,7,Fcosts such as energy inflation, rising
OL,8,Fprices for paint and other raw
OL,9,Fmaterials, rising courtesy car costs
OL,10,Fand the increased cost of second-hand
OL,11,Fcars as adding to overall cost
OL,12,Fpressures.
OL,14,FOver the longer term, motor insurance
OL,15,Fhas tracked very close to inflation,
OL,16,Fthe association said.
