OL,4,Cjumps by a third in a year
OL,6,FIn real terms, prices are #8 or 1.3%
OL,7,Fhigher when compared to a previous
OL,8,Fpeak at the end of 2017, according to
OL,9,Fthe ABI. This is partly because prices
OL,10,Ffell significantly during the
OL,11,Fcoronavirus pandemic, it said.
OL,13,FIt added that 2023 was a "difficult
OL,14,Fyear" for motor insurance margins, and
OL,15,Fthat since 2017, costs for insurers to
OL,16,Fpay claims have increased by 23% in
OL,17,Freal terms.
