OL,4,Cjumps by a third in a year
OL,6,FMervyn Skeet, the ABI's director of
OL,7,Fgeneral insurance policy, said: "We
OL,8,Funderstand that car insurance costs
OL,9,Fare putting pressure on household
OL,10,Ffinances. These figures show how
OL,11,Fcompetitive the motor market is, with
OL,12,Finsurers absorbing significant cost
OL,13,Frises but keeping prices relatively
OL,14,Fstable.
OL,16,F"Even though these figures demonstrate
OL,17,Fa slowdown in price increases, we
OL,18,Fwon't be taking our foot off the gas
OL,19,Fwhen it comes to our work on tackling
OL,20,Fthe cost of cover."
