OL,6,FThe ABI previously set out steps that
OL,7,Fthe industry is taking to combat the
OL,8,Frise in the cost of motor insurance in
OL,9,FFebruary. Last week it announced that
OL,10,Fits members had agreed a set of aimed
OL,11,Fat helping to manage the costs for
OL,12,Fpeople paying for insurance on a
OL,13,Fmonthly basis.
OL,15,FThe association said it recommends
OL,16,Fthat anyone struggling with the cost
OL,17,Fof their cover speaks to their insurer.
