OL,6,FIn another Treasury Committee session
OL,7,Flater that day, Charlotte Clark,
OL,8,Fdirector of regulation at the
OL,9,FAssociation of British Insurers (ABI),
OL,10,Ftold the committee that part of the
OL,11,Freason that rises in motor insurance
OL,12,Fmay look so significant is that "it's
OL,13,Fcoming off the back of the pandemic,
OL,14,Fwhere motor insurance in particular
OL,15,Fwas reduced quite significantly,
OL,16,Fbecause the risks of being in a car
OL,17,Faccident when you're at home are quite
OL,18,Flow".
