OL,6,FMatt Brewis, director of insurance at
OL,7,Fthe Financial Conduct Authority (FCA),
OL,8,Ftold the committee the regulator has
OL,9,Fbeen looking at evidence of how
OL,10,Finflation has impacted the motor
OL,11,Fsector.
OL,13,FHe said the regulator is meeting with
OL,14,Fprice comparison websites, brokers and
OL,15,Fconsumers "to understand the concerns
OL,16,Fof consumers and where they are seeing
OL,17,Fissues".
